# Cursor Rule: workflow

## Branching
- Feature branches: `feat/<short-scope>`
- Fix branches: `fix/<short-scope>`
- Chore: `chore/<scope>`

## Commits (Conventional)
- feat: user-facing change
- fix: bug fix
- chore/docs/test/build/refactor: as needed

## PR Requirements
- Link to PRD section or issue.
- Checklist: tests updated, lint passes, screenshots for UI changes.
- Include a brief “Why” and “Trade-offs”.

## Testing
- New logic → unit tests.
- Data access → happy + failure paths.
- UI → at least one interaction test per flow.
